  2420 				; ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  2421 				;  Per-voice level meters: 4 horizontal VU bars at scan 9-13, bar width =
  2422 				;  voice envelope level * 3 px. Drawn INCREMENTALLY -- each frame only the
  2423 				;  delta between the old and new level is set/cleared, so meters animating
  2424 				;  with the envelopes cost a few pixels per voice, not a full redraw.
  2425 				; ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
